# Parwana Beauty – Delete Account & Data Guide

**Last Updated:** 13th June 2026

Parwana Beauty respects your privacy and gives you full control over your account and personal data. This guide explains how you can request the deletion of your account and associated data.

---

## 1. How to Delete Your Account

To delete your Parwana Beauty account:

1. Log in to your Parwana Beauty account on our website or app.  
2. Send an email to **support@parwanabeauty.com** with the subject:  
   **Account Deletion Request**  
3. Include your **username or email address** associated with your account.  
4. Our team will process your request and confirm receipt within **24–48 hours**.  
5. Your account and all associated personal data (profile information, course progress, messages) will be permanently deleted within **30 days**.

---

## 2. Data Deleted

When you request account deletion, the following data will be removed:

- Personal information (name, email, username)  
- User progress and activity in courses  
- Uploaded assignments or files  
- Messages and forum posts (unless required by law to retain)  

---

## 3. Data Retention

Some data may be retained temporarily for legal or operational reasons:

- Backup logs and records for **up to 90 days** may be kept before permanent deletion  
- Data required for legal compliance may be retained as required  

---

## 4. Partial Data Deletion

Currently, Parwana Beauty **does not support partial deletion of data without deleting the account.**  
If you wish to remove specific information, contact **support@parwanabeauty.com** and our team will guide you.

---

## 5. Contact for Questions

If you have questions about data deletion or privacy policies, contact us:

- **Email:** support@parwanabeauty.com  
- **Website:** https://parwanabeauty.com/lms/
